程序包 org.janusgraph.graphdb

类 JanusGraphIterativeBenchmark

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.graphdb.JanusGraphBaseTest
org.janusgraph.graphdb.JanusGraphIterativeBenchmark
所有已实现的接口:
JanusGraphBaseStoreFeaturesTest
public abstract class JanusGraphIterativeBenchmark
extends JanusGraphBaseTest
A benchmark to test the performance of sequential row retrieval from the underlying KeyColumnValueStore which is the basic operation underlying the Fulgora OLAP component of JanusGraph.

Hence, this is effectively a benchmark for OLAPTest or at least the primitive backend operations used therein.

作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
